#TheReviewPoint


Border 2 trailer has finally arrived and it delivers pure deshbhakti, emotions and mass cinema at its peak. Sunny Deol returns with the same thunderous aura, powerful dialogues and unmatched intensity that made Border (1997) a cult classic.

From goosebumps-inducing dialogues to grand war scale, Border 2 trailer proves this is not just a sequel but a legacy revival. Varun Dhawan brings controlled aggression, Diljit Dosanjh adds soul, and the Army‚ÄìNavy‚ÄìAir Force unity gives pure patriotic highs.

This Republic Day 2026 release is shaping up to be a massive box office storm. With Sunny Deol owning every frame, Border 2 is built for theatres, whistles, claps and national pride.

Is Border 2 the biggest war film ever made in Hindi cinema?
Can Sunny Deol deliver another historic blockbuster?

Watch this full Border 2 trailer review for detailed breakdown, emotional analysis, dialogues impact, scale discussion and box office prediction.

snippet.title: Team of the Year is Here! RIP TOTY?
snippet.description:
The new Team of the Year (TOTY) event is here, and it is a disaster. Today, I expose everything wrong with FC Mobile 26.

In this video, I break down why the New Draft System is a scam and why the removal of Store Packs destroys the Free-to-Play (F2P) experience. I also expose the terrible exchange rates for Phase 2 Tokens and Market Pick Tokens (only 5 tokens for a 115 OVR?!).

To prove my point, I spend my 10 Free Draft Vouchers on few different accounts and show you the pack probabilities. I am officially starting the #FixFCMobileTOTY movement. Until EA Sports fixes these issues, I will not be spending any FC Points or Gems.

Celebrate the auspicious occasion of Kanuma 2026 on this holy Friday with these divine Lakshmi Devi Bhakti Songs. While Kanuma is famously known as Pasuvula Panduga (Festival of Cattle), worshipping Goddess Mahalakshmi on a Friday during the Sankranti season is believed to bring double the blessings of wealth and prosperity.

Listening to these powerful chants like Ashta Lakshmi Stotram, Kanakadhara Stotram, and Sri Lakshmi Ashtakam helps remove financial difficulties ("Daridrya Nashanam") and invites "Ashta Aishwaryalu" into your home. In our tradition, the cow (Gomatha) is also worshipped as a form of Lakshmi. Therefore, playing these Friday Special God Songs on Kanuma is considered extremely sacred.

Whether you are performing Tulasi Pooja, Go Pooja, or simply lighting the evening lamp, let these melodious Ammavari Patalu fill your home with peace. May the Mother of Wealth bless you with a debt-free and prosperous life

snippet.title: I Survived the Unstable SMP Purge
snippet.description:
Following the first round of the Unstable SMP election, LettuceK called all the remaining candidates into the banquet hall to make an announcement. Nobody could have prepared for what was about to happen next. This is How I Survived the Unstable SMP Purge.

Unstable SMP:
‚ûú ‚Ä™ @Spokeishere 
‚ûú ‚Ä™ @wemmbumc 
‚ûú ‚Ä™ @FlameFragsMC 
‚ûú ‚Ä™ @ParrotX2 

Like ParrotX2 and his Unstable SMP series, where he is escaping Paragon / Proton: Minecraft's Most Secure Prison, or got hunted by a Minecraft Player who doesn't exist. This is a new and original Minecraft idea like HermitCraft or Lifesteal with Wemmbu, FlameFrags, or Spoke. Survival is harder than Hardcore Minecraft because PVP is on.

People in this video: @LettuceK @TheobaldTheBird @PurpledMC @fymada @HoraceMinecraft @Boosfer @naparizel 

Original music by @tsynphonia

snippet.title: THE BRIDE! | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Are you ready for.....THE BRIDE!? #TheBrideMovie only in theaters and IMAX March 6. #FilmedForIMAX

Trailer Music by Florence + The Machine, listen to ‚ÄúEverybody Scream‚Äù https://florence.lnk.to/everybodyscream-song

From Maggie Gyllenhaal (Academy Award-nominated writer/director of The Lost Daughter) and starring Academy Award nominee Jessie Buckley and Academy Award winner Christian Bale comes THE BRIDE! A bold, iconoclastic take on one of the world‚Äôs most compelling stories.

A lonely Frankenstein (Bale) travels to 1930s Chicago to ask groundbreaking scientist Dr. Euphronious (five-time Oscar nominee Annette Bening) to create a companion for him. The two revive a murdered young woman and The Bride (Buckley) is born. What ensues is beyond what either of them imagined: Murder! Possession! A wild and radical cultural movement! And outlaw lovers in a wild and combustible romance!

The film stars Buckley, Bale, Peter Sarsgaard, with Bening, Academy Award nominee Jake Gyllenhaal, and Oscar winner Pen√©lope Cruz. Maggie Gyllenhaal directs from her own screenplay and produces alongside Oscar nominee Emma Tillinger Koskoff, Talia Kleinhendler and Osnat Handelsman Keren. snippet.title: Chowkidar Official Trailer [Kannada] | Pruthvi Ambaar | Sai Kumar | Dhanya Ramkumar | Sachin Basrur
snippet.description:
Presenting the official trailer of "Chowkidar", an intense action-drama that explores the thin line between duty and defiance. Starring the versatile Pruthvi Ambaar in a never-seen-before mass avatar and the 'Dialogue King' Sai Kumar in a powerful role, Chowkidar is set to be a cinematic feast for Kannada audiences.

Adding to the intensity is the brilliant Dhanya Ramkumar, with a soul-stirring background score and music by the sensation Sachin Basrur. Get ready for a story of grit, mystery, and raw power!
